4
00:00:23,280 --> 00:00:27,320
Did you notice anything unusual
grammatically about what she,

5
00:00:27,320 --> 00:00:30,800
I just said?
When did all this happen?

6
00:00:30,800 --> 00:00:34,160
So yesterday morning.
I'm running a bit late . 

7
00:00:34,160 --> 00:00:36,640
Yesterday morning.
So it's past, right?

8
00:00:36,640 --> 00:00:40,920
OK, so listen again. How many
past verb forms can you hear?

9
