11
00:00:51,040 --> 00:00:56,320
Thank you, Joanne.
Right, let's look at the score.

12
00:00:56,440 --> 00:00:59,520
Now would you look at that:

13
00:00:59,520 --> 00:01:02,040
zero, nil, nothing,
zilch, nought.

14
00:01:02,040 --> 00:01:05,400
I think we can agree that
